# ---------------
# Colour settings
# ===============

Colorset 0  fg #ffffff, bg #003c3c
Colorset 1  fg #000000, bg #dfa700
Colorset 2  fg #ffffff, bg #3c0000
MenuStyle * MenuColorset 0
*FvwmButtons: Colorset 0
*FvwmPager: Colorset '*' 0
*FvwmPager: WindowColorsets '*' 1
*FvwmPager: HilightColorset '*' 1
*FvwmPager: SloppyFocus

Style "FvwmButtons" StaysOnTop
#Style "FvwmIconMan" StaysOnTop

